    Serializable, Map

    public final class StormConfig
extends org.apache.flink.api.common.ExecutionConfig.GlobalJobParameters
implements Map
    StormConfig is used to provide a user-defined Storm configuration (ie, a raw Map or Config object) for embedded Spouts and Bolts.
